document.title: Hybrid Poplar Field Day
document.abstract: UT Extension hosts Heritage Skills in Crossville each year. The above is one of the completed baskets made in 10-14 in the White Oak Basket Seminar. We take the baskets outside and look for a good photo op place. The baskets against the wood were great!
